chart_description: The IP Bandwidth chart shows the amount of network traffic in kilobits per second (kbps) for incoming and outgoing data (InOctets and OutOctets) over the network interface.

dimension_descriptions.InOctets: The amount of incoming data in kilobits per second on the network interface.
dimension_descriptions.OutOctets: The amount of outgoing data in kilobits per second on the network interface.
